name: Still Alive
blurb: A fresh twist on survival games. Intense, high-stakes 30 minute rounds for up to 10 players.

rewards.reward: *EMERGENCY SUPPLY* - Thank you for your support! - You get the Still Alive wallpaper as well as a mention in the game credits.
*RADIO OPERATOR* - \r\nYou get a digital copy of the \u201cStill Alive\u201c soundtrack, a wallpaper as well as a mention in the game credits.
*BASIC EQUIPMENT - EARLY BIRD*\r\nWith your pledge of $10 you get a digital copy of the game for a limited early bird price and of course a mention in the game credits.
*BASIC EQUIPMENT* -\r\nYou get a digital copy of the game and a mention in the game credits.
*FREQUENCY AMPLIFIER* - \r\nYou get a digital copy of the game including the soundtrack and a mention in the game credits.

*(BUG-) HUNTSMAN KIT - EARLY BIRD* - \r\nBe part of the closed \u201cStill Alive\u201c beta (PC Only). Get a beta key and access to the beta forum for the limited early bird price. You will also be mentioned as a beta tester in the game credits.
*(BUG-) HUNTSMAN KIT* -\r\nBe part of the closed \u201cStill Alive\u201c beta (PC Only). Get a beta key and access to the beta forum.\r\nAlso you are mentioned as a beta tester in the game credits.

*TWO-MAN TENT* -\r\nDon\u2019t die alone \u2013 bring a buddy! You get one digital copy of the game and soundtrack for yourself and an additional copy of the game and soundtrack to give to your friend.

*SURVIVOR\u00b4S KIT - EARLY BIRD* -\r\nBe the first to test the game. You get early access to the alpha version of the game (PC Only).\r\nAdditionally you get access to the developer forum, a digital copy of the soundtrack and a digital survival handbook. All that for this limited early bird price.
*SURVIVOR\u00b4S KIT* - access to the alpha version of the game (PC Only).\r\nAdditionally you get access to the developer forum, a digital copy of the soundtrack and a digital survival handbook.

*SPARE CLOTHES KIT* - \r\nYou get 1 of the 2 Kickstarter exclusive skin packs to choose from. These skins will not be available to anyone after the Kickstarter period. You also get all goodies from the Survivor\u2019s Kit.

*PORTABLE WARDROBE - EARLY BIRD* -\r\nYou get both of the Kickstarter exclusive skin packs. These skins will not be available to anyone after the Kickstarter period. You also get the goodies from the Survivor\u2019s Kit and all that for the early bird price of your $75 pledge.

*PORTABLE WARDROBE* - You get both of the Kickstarter exclusive skin packs. These skins will not be available to anyone after the Kickstarter period. You also get the goodies from the Survivor\u2019s Kit.
*PAINTBOX* - \r\nDesign a graffiti or poster with us, which will be implemented in the game (within good taste)!\r\nYou also get everything from the Portable Wardrobe set.

*SEWING MACHINE* - \r\nDesign a skin with us the way you like (within good taste of course). This skin is exclusive for you to use. Additionally you get 4 early alpha keys with your designed skin to give away. You also get everything from the Portable Wardrobe.

*SHELTER* - \r\nSend us a picture or sketch of your room and we will implement it in a level in \u201cStill Alive\u201d! So you can actually play in your room while you play in your room! Additionally you get 4 early alpha keys to give away and everything from the Portable Wardrobe.

*CAPITALIST KIT* - \r\nAs our most generous backer you will get a big in-game billboard designed by the Binji team according to your wishes (within good taste of course). This will be totally unique and will be placed in a good visible spot in the level.\r\nAdditionally you get everything from the Portable Wardrobe. You will be mentioned in the game credits as our capitalist support.
